Package: samplesizr
Type: Package
Title: Sample-size calculation made simple
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Daniel Goseberg
Maintainer: Daniel Goseberg <goseberg.d@gmail.com>
Description: Samplesizr. Based on the book M. Kieser: Fallzahlberechnung 
    in der medizinischen Forschung (2018).
    This macro deploys functions to compute the sample size for
    clinical trials in different situations. There are functions
    for comparing groups with normal distributed (z-test, t-test,
    ANCOVA, f-test) or binary data (Chi-Square-test, Fisher-Boschloo-
    test).
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: MASS, stats, BiasedUrn
Suggests: testthat
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
